e3500488271' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery.min.js?ver=3.7.1\" id=\"jquery-core-js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery-migrate.min.js?ver=3.4.1\" id=\"jquery-migrate-js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"https://api.w.org/\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wp-json/\" /><link rel=\"alternate\" title=\"JSON\" type=\"application/json\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wp-json/wp/v2/pages/1012\" /><link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" title=\"RSD\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/xmlrpc.php?rsd\" />\n\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/welfare\" />\n<link rel='shortlink' href='https://www.nj-aac.com/?p=1012' />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" title=\"oEmbed (JSON)\" type=\"application/json+oembed\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nj-aac.com%2Frecruit%2Fwelfare\" />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" title=\"oEmbed (XML)\" type=\"text/xml+oembed\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nj-aac.com%2Frecruit%2Fwelfare&#038;format=xml\" />\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body class=\"wp-singular page-template page-template-page-temp-recruit-child page-template-page-temp-recruit-child-php page page-id-1012 page-child parent-pageid-46 wp-theme-nj-aac welfare\">\r\n\t<div class=\"site-header\" id=\"ancher-top\">\r\n\t\t<header class=\"site-header--fixed\">\r\n\t\t\t<a class=\"recruit-header-logo\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit\"><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/header-logo-recruit.png\" alt=\"株式会社 北日本朝日航洋\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"header-nav-wrap\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-toggle menu\" id=\"nav-toggle\"><span class=\"icon\"></span></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t<nav class=\"header-nav header-nav-recruit\" id=\"header-nav\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"menu\"><li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1015\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/seek\">求める人材</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1016\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/oneday\">先輩社員の一日</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page current-menu-item page_item page-item-1012 current_page_item menu-item-1019\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/welfare\" aria-current=\"page\">福利厚生</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1017\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/requirements\">募集要項</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item-contact menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1018\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/contact\">エントリー / お問い合わせ</a></li>\n</ul>\t\t\t\t</nav>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"nav-bg\" class=\"nav-bg\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</header>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<div class=\"recruit-site-content\">\r\n\r\n\t\t<div class=\"page-title\">\r\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"title\">福利厚生</h1>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t\t        <div class=\"breadcrumb inner\">\r\n            <ol>\r\n            <li><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com\">ホーム</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit\">採用情報</a></li><li>福利厚生</li>            </ol>\r\n        </div>\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t<main class=\"main\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>トヨタ販売連合健康保険組合（直営保養所(京都・嵐山)）</li>\n\n\n\n<li>健康保険・厚生年金・雇用保険・労災保険</li>\n\n\n\n<li>エアロトヨタグル－プ共済会制度</li>\n\n\n\n<li>トヨタグル－プ団体自動車保険（割引有）他各種傷害保険</li>\n\n\n\n<li>団体長期障害所得補償保険</li>\n\n\n\n<li>メンター制度(入社後1年間)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>資格取得支援制度(入社後)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-title3\">取得可能資格</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul id=\"block-ec28577e-24fc-461d-a034-29d2a7a46469\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>測量士</li>\n\n\n\n<li>技術士</li>\n\n\n\n<li>RCCM</li>\n\n\n\n<li>基本情報技術者</li>\n\n\n\n<li>土地家屋調査士</li>\n\n\n\n<li>宅地建物取引士</li>\n\n\n\n<li>土木施工管理技士</li>\n\n\n\n<li>地籍調査管理技術者</li>\n\n\n\n<li>補償業務管理士</li>\n\n\n\n<li>個人情報保護士等</li>\n</ul>\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t</main>\r\n\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<footer class=\"site-footer\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"footer-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"footer-nav\"><li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-home menu-item-1020\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/\">北日本朝日航洋公式サイト</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1021\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/company\">企業情報</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1023\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/company/securitypolicy\">情報セキュリティポリシー</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1022\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/company/privacypolicy\">個人情報保護方針</a></li>\n</ul>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"footer-address\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"logos\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://privacymark.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-privacy.jpg?2\" alt=\"プライバシーマーク\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/seisakunitsuite/bunya/kodomo/shokuba_kosodate/kurumin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-kurumin2022.jpg\" alt=\"くるみんマーク\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-health-and-productivity-2024.jpg\" alt=\"健康経営優良法人2024\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-ikusei-r6.jpg\" alt=\"いわて産業人材奨学金返還支援制度\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<p>北日本朝日航洋は、プライバシーマーク、くるみんマーク、健康経営優良法人、いわて産業人材奨学金返還支援制度の認定を取得しています。</p>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<small class=\"copyright\">&copy;2010-2021 North Japan Aero Asahi Corporation</small>\r\n\t</footer>\r\n\r\n\t<script type=\"specul